Notes: 1953 15 M A21 Thames DHS 4 BEAUTY LIKE A LOLLY -->ca1953 H.S. Gajadhar (Auckland), `Beautee @/bju:t : :/ is the usual pronunciation in all senses.' -->ca1953 July (Chateau Tongariro Hotel), @/bju:t : / continually from a billiard-player after making a good shot. -->1951 14 M 10 Wellington H.S. 18 BEAUTY [exclam. of delight] -->1953 14-17 M A16 Thames DHS 18 BEAUTY [M4] -->1984 16 M E77 Pakuranga Coll. 35A BEAUTY [exclam. of approval]
